				<Node aliases="PMOD" mnemonic="PMODe">
					<SubsystemCommand>
						<Synopsis>This command sets the preferred mode for output on or output off transitions. It allows output state transitions to be optimized for either constant voltage or constant current operation. Turn-on and turn-off overshoots are minimized for the preferred mode of operation.</Synopsis>
