						<Synopsis>This query returns the value of the Questionable Status Condition register. The Condition register is a read-only register, which holds the live (unlatched) questionable status of the instrument. Reading the Questionable Condition register does not clear it.</Synopsis>
						<HelpLinks>
							<HelpLink name="STATus:QUEStionable:CONDition?" url="STATus_Subsystem\STATus_QUEStionable_CONDition_.htm" />
